Hello, this is one of my gungame maps and i hope you like it. There is a total of 36 spawns. Each team has 18 spawn points. I made a cover at door so that snipers (AKA. Spawn killers) don't sit there and keep killing you. You are able to shoot through some walls. If you have any further problems or ideas for the next update please contact me at bloodyheadshot914@yahoo.com.

Thankyou,
Genocide
